# License

This repository consists of 2 differently-licensed parts.

## 1. Sample texts

As agreed on the Mozilla's [Common Voice Legal Terms](https://voice.mozilla.org/en/terms), all sample texts, recordings, as well as datasets are under Public Domain or in similar license, especially Creative Commons CC0 1.0 Universal (CC-0).

The full license script is found at LICENSE-CC0.txt.

## 2. Word Counting Scripts

All files located under the `scripts/` folder are licensed under the MIT License (instead of Mozilla Public License 2.0).
